{"tid":1666771,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"讀OU不如讀asso","createTime":"2019-10-21T06:25:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T02:41:03.000Z","uid":300013,"like":73,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"f40113e499f6fa932e65c5b8aa4a3ee77e65f295","tid":1666771,"uid":300013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:25:13.000Z","msg":"真係唔係講笑。<br />\n<br />\n鯨大同八大d課程難度真係相差好大。真係唔明點解有人可以將鯨大 1st hon &gt; 三大1st hon。完全唔係一個level。希望某d人可以謙虛d。<br />\n<br />\n如果真係有心讀上去，我寧願你讀asso，都唔好自資學士（鯨大）。就算你將來想tran U都係咁話。因為OU真係好浪費時間。一個sem讀四科都算，d嘢又淺。其他asso升上黎嘅同學，好多課都學過。OU係好多都係白紙。<br />\n<br />\n真係唔明OU兩年讀四科GE，用黎做咩？<br />\n<br />\n用OU兩年知識，硬接八大yr 3真係好痴線。唔係唔得，但係會好chur。追cre都追到你痴線，如果要準時畢業。<br />\n<br />\n唔好話打手喇。以上係真實經歷。<br />\n<br />\n利申：鯨大tran又一城"},{"pid":"cca6dcd81cd4253dfad5f23d9f8654a1b7f4a819","tid":1666771,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:25:28.000Z","msg":"不如全港黨鐵靜坐聲討721啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665580</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"766435a9cc8b940f4c5588cb9bd31f80fb86a9eb","tid":1666771,"uid":81698,"like":24,"dislike":3,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:30:33.000Z","msg":"開完取暖post未？得啦shitty仔唔洗讀鯨大啦知啦<br />\n唔洗開咁多個post搵存在感"},{"pid":"1b30e585b0cf23769c5ee0f12e2f697520ed6bb5","tid":1666771,"uid":300013,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"quote":{"pid":"766435a9cc8b940f4c5588cb9bd31f80fb86a9eb","tid":1666771,"uid":81698,"like":24,"dislike":3,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:30:33.000Z","msg":"開完取暖post未？得啦shitty仔唔洗讀鯨大啦知啦<br />\n唔洗開咁多個post搵存在感"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:37:53.000Z","msg":"唔知踩親你邊條尾<br />\n提醒人唔好中伏都有錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你唔知幾多人自資學士同asso向左走向右走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f119b8fee09f41d5e5af0fc133f06